{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775853736311,"sessionID":"ses_286e015c3ffetU3z6nz1otpb4p","part":{"id":"prt_d7920a6d1001kkbehnxURAKvUB","messageID":"msg_d79207cde001t795yiMDSnxqWc","sessionID":"ses_286e015c3ffetU3z6nz1otpb4p","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-6ed2f366066149a2b7a8babf79658978","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/spec.md","content":"# AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/store` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n\n定义会话存储的抽象接口和数据结构，包括:\n- `SessionStore` 接口定义\n- `Session` 数据结构\n- 存储操作方法签名\n\n## Out of Scope\n\n- 具体存储实现 (Redis、Memory 等)\n- 存储连接池管理\n- 分布式锁实现\n\n## Dependencies\n\n无外部依赖。\n\n## Deliverables\n\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `pkg/store/store.go` | SessionStore 接口定义 |\n| `pkg/store/session.go` | Session 数据结构 |\n| `pkg/store/doc.go` | 包文档 |\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] 接口定义完整\n- [ ] Session 数据结构包含必要字段\n- [ ] 通过 `go vet` 和 `golangci-lint`\n\n## References\n\n- 待补充"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/spec.md","time":{"start":1775853736285,"end":1775853736310}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775853736313,"sessionID":"ses_286e015c3ffetU3z6nz1otpb4p","part":{"id":"prt_d7920f65b001TDdtw8kexTtQJm","messageID":"msg_d79207cde001t795yiMDSnxqWc","sessionID":"ses_286e015c3ffetU3z6nz1otpb4p","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-86cbe5251bba4627aebce78284047c03","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/proposal.md","content":"# AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 Proposal\n\n## Purpose\n\n定义会话存储的抽象接口层，为 AgentCube 的会话管理提供统一的存储抽象。该接口设计遵循以下原则:\n\n1. **接口抽象**: 定义标准 CRUD 操作接口，支持多种存储后端实现\n2. **数据结构**: Session 结构包含会话标识、状态、生命周期等核心字段\n3. **扩展性**: 接口设计支持未来扩展 (如批量操作、事务支持)\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n| Deliverable | Description |\n|-------------|-------------|\n| `pkg/store/store.go` | SessionStore 接口定义，包含 CRUD 方法签名 |\n| `pkg/store/session.go` | Session 数据结构，包含必要字段定义 |\n| `pkg/store/doc.go` | 包文档 |\n\n### Out of Scope\n\n- 具体存储实现 (Redis、Memory、Etcd 等)\n- 存储连接池管理\n- 分布式锁实现\n- 缓存策略\n- 存储健康检查\n\n## Impact Analysis\n\n### Upstream Dependencies\n\n| Dependency | Impact |\n|------------|--------|\n| `time` | Session 生命周期时间字段 |\n| `context` | 操作上下文传递 |\n\n### Downstream Consumers\n\n| Consumer | Usage |\n|----------|-------|\n| Session Manager | 使用 SessionStore 接口管理会话 |\n| Router | 通过 SessionStore 查询会话状态 |\n| Workload Manager | 创建/更新会话状态 |\n| 存储实现模块 | 实现 SessionStore 接口 |\n\n### Breaking Change Considerations\n\n- **接口签名变更**: 新增/修改方法签名会影响所有实现\n- **Session 字段变更**: 添加/删除字段需同步所有消费者\n- **错误类型变更**: 返回错误类型变更需消费者适配\n\n## Alternatives Considered\n\n### Alternative 1: 直接使用 Redis Client\n\n**Approach**: 不定义抽象接口，直接在各模块使用 Redis 客户端。\n\n| Aspect | Evaluation |\n|--------|------------|\n| Pros | 简单直接，减少抽象层 |\n| Cons | 无法切换存储后端；测试困难；Redis 依赖渗透 |\n\n**Decision**: Rejected. 接口抽象支持多后端实现和测试 mock。\n\n### Alternative 2: 使用第三方存储库\n\n**Approach**: 使用如 `gocache` 等第三方存储抽象库。\n\n| Aspect | Evaluation |\n|--------|------------|\n| Pros | 功能完善，社区支持 |\n| Cons | 过度依赖；接口可能不匹配 AgentCube 需求 |\n\n**Decision**: Rejected. AgentCube 需求简单，自定义接口更灵活。\n\n## Risks\n\n| Risk | Mitigation |\n|------|------------|\n| 接口设计不完整 | 参考现有 Session Manager 使用场景 |\n| Session 字段遗漏 | 核对 Router/Workload Manager 需求 |\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n1. 接口方法返回 error，支持自定义错误类型\n2. Session 结构使用时间戳而非 Duration，便于存储\n3. 使用 context.Context 支持操作超时和取消\n\n## References\n\n- 待补充"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/proposal.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775853736292,"end":1775853736311}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775853736314,"sessionID":"ses_286e015c3ffetU3z6nz1otpb4p","part":{"id":"prt_d79214311001lUhnXOVZEcc9IP","messageID":"msg_d79207cde001t795yiMDSnxqWc","sessionID":"ses_286e015c3ffetU3z6nz1otpb4p","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-f648c5ce270a4d2d9bb147e1c1d70b8b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/design.md","content":"# AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/store` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n定义会话存储的抽象接口层，为 Session Manager 提供统一的存储操作接口。\n\n## Design\n\n### Architecture\n\n接口设计遵循 Go 接口惯例:\n- 方法签名简洁，返回 error\n- 使用 context.Context 支持超时/取消\n- Session 结构可序列化，支持多种存储后端\n\n### Dependencies\n\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|\n| `context` | 操作上下文 |\n| `time` | 时间字段 |\n\n## Data Structures\n\n### SessionStore Interface\n\n```go\ntype SessionStore interface {\n    Create(ctx context.Context, session *Session) error\n    Get(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*Session, error)\n    Update(ctx context.Context, session *Session) error\n    Delete(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n    List(ctx context.Context, filter *SessionFilter) ([]*Session, error)\n}\n```\n\n### Session\n\n```go\ntype Session struct {\n    ID           string    `json:\"id\"`\n    SandboxID    string    `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n    Namespace    string    `json:\"namespace\"`\n    Name         string    `json:\"name\"`\n    Status       string    `json:\"status\"`\n    CreatedAt    time.Time `json:\"createdAt\"`\n    UpdatedAt    time.Time `json:\"updatedAt\"`\n    ExpiresAt    time.Time `json:\"expiresAt\"`\n    LastActiveAt time.Time `json:\"lastActiveAt\"`\n}\n```\n\n### SessionFilter\n\n```go\ntype SessionFilter struct {\n    Namespace string\n    Status    string\n    Name      string\n}\n```\n\n## API Contracts\n\n### Create\n\n```go\nfunc Create(ctx context.Context, session *Session) error\n```\n- Input: Session pointer with required fields populated\n- Output: error on failure, nil on success\n\n### Get\n\n```go\nfunc Get(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*Session, error)\n```\n- Input: sessionID string\n- Output: Session pointer, error (including NotFound error)\n\n### Update\n\n```go\nfunc Update(ctx context.Context, session *Session) error\n```\n- Input: Session pointer with updated fields\n- Output: error on failure, nil on success\n\n### Delete\n\n```go\nfunc Delete(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n```\n- Input: sessionID string\n- Output: error on failure, nil on success\n\n### List\n\n```go\nfunc List(ctx context.Context, filter *SessionFilter) ([]*Session, error)\n```\n- Input: optional SessionFilter\n- Output: slice of Session pointers, error\n\n## Error Handling\n\n建议定义自定义错误类型:\n- `SessionNotFoundError` - 会话不存在\n- `SessionAlreadyExistsError` - 会话已存在\n- `SessionStoreError` - 存储操作失败\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### Unit Tests\n\n| Test Category | Coverage |\n|---------------|----------|\n| Session 结构序列化 | JSON 序列化/反序列化正确 |\n| SessionFilter 过滤 | 过滤字段正确匹配 |\n\n### Integration Tests\n\n- Mock 实现测试接口契约\n- 真实存储实现验证 (后续实现模块)\n\n### Test Utilities\n\n```go\ntype MockSessionStore struct {\n    sessions map[string]*Session\n    // 实现所有接口方法\n}\n```\n\n## File Structure\n\n```\npkg/store/\n  store.go     — SessionStore 接口定义\n  session.go   — Session、SessionFilter 数据结构\n  doc.go       — 包文档\n```\n\n## Open Questions\n\n- 是否需要支持批量操作 (BatchCreate/BatchDelete)?\n- 是否需要支持事务操作?\n- SessionFilter 是否需要更多过滤字段?\n\n## References\n\n- 待补充"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/design.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/design.md","time":{"start":1775853736297,"end":1775853736313}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775853736317,"sessionID":"ses_286e015c3ffetU3z6nz1otpb4p","part":{"id":"prt_d792191460014QFg6mZjK3YSQH","messageID":"msg_d79207cde001t795yiMDSnxqWc","sessionID":"ses_286e015c3ffetU3z6nz1otpb4p","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-96b9c74096e745d586067fc1e1368998","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/tasks.md","content":"# AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/store` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Design | [Stage ST-0] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Project Setup\n\n- [ ] **T1.1** Create directory structure `pkg/store/`\n- [ ] **T1.2** Verify Go module exists and add dependencies if needed\n\n### Phase 2: Core Type Definitions\n\n- [ ] **T2.1** Create `pkg/store/doc.go`\n  - Add package documentation\n  - Describe store module purpose\n\n- [ ] **T2.2** Create `pkg/store/session.go`\n  - Define `Session` struct with fields:\n    - `ID string`\n    - `SandboxID string`\n    - `Namespace string`\n    - `Name string`\n    - `Status string`\n    - `CreatedAt time.Time`\n    - `UpdatedAt time.Time`\n    - `ExpiresAt time.Time`\n    - `LastActiveAt time.Time`\n  - Add JSON tags for serialization\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/store/`\n\n- [ ] **T2.3** Create `pkg/store/store.go`\n  - Define `SessionStore` interface with methods:\n    - `Create(ctx, session) error`\n    - `Get(ctx, sessionID) (*Session, error)`\n    - `Update(ctx, session) error`\n    - `Delete(ctx, sessionID) error`\n    - `List(ctx, filter) ([]*Session, error)`\n  - Define `SessionFilter` struct for list filtering\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/store/`\n\n### Phase 3: Error Types (Optional)\n\n- [ ] **T3.1** Define custom error types in `pkg/store/errors.go`\n  - `SessionNotFoundError`\n  - `SessionAlreadyExistsError`\n  - `SessionStoreError`\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/store/`\n\n### Phase 4: Unit Tests\n\n- [ ] **T4.1** Create `pkg/store/session_test.go`\n  - Test Session struct JSON serialization/deserialization\n  - Test SessionFilter with various filter combinations\n  - Verify: `go test ./pkg/store/... -v`\n\n### Phase 5: Validation & Quality\n\n- [ ] **T5.1** Run `go vet ./pkg/store/...`\n  - Fix any issues reported\n\n- [ ] **T5.2** Run `golangci-lint run ./pkg/store/...`\n  - Fix any linting issues\n\n- [ ] **T5.3** Verify JSON tags use camelCase\n  - Check: `sandboxId`, `createdAt`, `updatedAt`, `expiresAt`, `lastActiveAt`\n\n---\n\n## Task Dependencies\n\n```\nT1.1 → T1.2 → T2.1 → T2.2 → T2.3 → T3.1 → T4.1 → T5.1 → T5.2 → T5.3\n```\n\n---\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n| Task | Verification Command |\n|------|----------------------|\n| T1.2 | `go mod tidy && go mod verify` |\n| T2.1-T2.3 | `go build ./pkg/store/...` |\n| T3.1 | `go build ./pkg/store/...` |\n| T4.1 | `go test ./pkg/store/... -v -cover` |\n| T5.1 | `go vet ./pkg/store/...` |\n| T5.2 | `golangci-lint run ./pkg/store/...` |\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] SessionStore 接口定义完整\n- [ ] Session 数据结构包含必要字段\n- [ ] SessionFilter 支持基本过滤\n- [ ] Pass `go vet` with zero issues\n- [ ] Pass `golangci-lint` with zero issues\n- [ ] JSON tags 使用 camelCase\n- [ ] Unit tests pass\n\n---\n\n## Notes\n\n- 仅定义接口，不实现具体存储逻辑\n- 具体实现由后续 AR 提供 (如 Redis 实现)\n- 接口设计参考 Session Manager 使用场景\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Timeline\n\n| Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n|-------|-------|--------|------------|\n| Phase 1: Project Setup | T1.1-T1.2 | Not Started | 0% |\n| Phase 2: Core Type Definitions | T2.1-T2.3 | Not Started | 0% |\n| Phase 3: Error Types | T3.1 | Not Started | 0% |\n| Phase 4: Unit Tests | T4.1 | Not Started | 0% |\n| Phase 5: Validation | T5.1-T5.3 | Not Started | 0% |\n\n**Total Progress: 0% Complete**"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_